message.body: Hey lady will u be around Xmas day? I'm going to my mums and want to go out with people at night!
Yeah! Adam and i should be at my parents or his. Let's do it! I have to work at 5am the next day though, so we can't stay too late.
Ok! I want a lot of people to go to one place, make it easy peasy! Like shamrock?
Ha. I don't know if Adam is allowed in there! That'd be good though, it's right by our house.
Hahahaha..yeah I was nervous last time I went, I had memories of being blacklisted. I'm bringing my bf to lanc with me for the first time, want to give him the full experience ha
Oh dear...is he ready?
No he has absolutely no idea how ratty things can get
Geez. Are you sure you want to take him to the shamrock? Are you sure you want Adam and i going? (kidding.)
Haha! Of course lovey! Plus, being able to hang is mandatory! I went to his stuffy office party with him, haha
Ha ha ha!!
I'm so charming haha. School is good for me, semester ended today happy happy happy. How are u?
Oh not bad. Work a lot of crazy hours which is exhausting! But I'm ok. Money makin...
Yeah, five am, yikes! Where are u working?
The marriott downtown
I work as a telephone operator. I get to wear a blazer and have a 401k. Very fancy. Haha. Seriously, I'm just waiting on rich folks in a new facet...
Wow, a blazer! Are you the operator that answers calls from the rooms? Ha, we are always just waiting on rich people
Yeah, incoming calls, inter hotel calls, calls from guests. It's either really stressful or really boring. Today I'm getting paid to play on the internet
... Speaking of which: is there anything you can suggest? I'm mega bored.
Those are two terrible extremes...when I'm bored I like to look at rich kids of Instagram haha
Hmmm. Good idea! Vice often has interesting photos too. Good ol vice.
